      "role": "user",
      "content": "but isn't the whole point of \"natural\" stuff that it's safer? like if i'm already feeling these withdrawal symptoms/side effects from the zoloft, shouldn't i just get the serotonin levels back up with the herb so i dont crash? i just want a straight answer on whether combining them during a taper is actually dangerous or if people do it all the time to make the transition easier. i really need to know if this is a viable way to switch so i can stop feeling like this",
